                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8134" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1264</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3044 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">易普力成功借壳，“炸”出央地合作新典范</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EXPLOSIVES Co.,Ltd successfully backdoor to open up a new model of central-local cooperation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐维东，童子馨，王仅尔，王一多</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">易普力股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">易普力；分拆+借壳上市；央地联合；重大资产重组</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EXPLOSIVES Co.,Ltd; Spin-off+backdoor; Central-local linkage;  Asset reorganization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着国企改革三年行动进入收官之年，民爆行业国企积极开展业务重组整合。本文选取中国能建分拆子公司易普力并借壳南岭民爆上市为案例，首先介绍了民爆行业及国企改革背景，包括参与重组三方的基本情况；其次，梳理回顾了“分拆+借壳”事件的全过程以及企业未来整合计划；最后，凝练此次重组事件的影响及意义，关注其在开展央地合作重组后跃升行业龙头的先锋典范作用。本文旨在通过该重大无先例案例，帮助学生了解国有企业“分拆+借壳”上市的动因、明晰借壳交易方案的设计以及并购事项的推进过程，引导学生深入思考A+H股上市公司借壳的资本运作历程，了解跨地区“央企+地方国企”的重组整合效果和未来央地联合的新方向，具有极强的创新意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the three-year action plan for state-owned enterprise reform entering its final year, state-owned enterprises in the civil explosive industry actively carry out business restructuring and integration. This article takes the listing of EXPLOSIVES Co.,Ltd, a subsidiary of China Energy Engineering Co.,Ltd, by acquiring and merging with Hunan Nanling Industry Explosive Material Co.,Ltd. as a case study. Firstly, it introduces the background of the civilian explosives industry and state-owned enterprise reform, includingthe basic situation of the three parties involved in the reorganization. Secondly, it reviews the entire process of the &quot;spin-off + backdoor&quot; event and the company&#39;s future integration plan. Finally, it summarizes the impact and significance of this reorganization event and focuses on its pioneering role in becoming a leading company in the industry through central and local cooperation. The aim of this article is to help students understand the reasons for state-owned enterprises listing through &quot;spin-off + backdoor&quot; , clarify the design of backdoor transaction plan, and realize the process of mergers and acquisitions. This will lead students to think deeply about the capital operation process of A+H listed companies through backdoor, understand the effect of cross-regional &quot;central enterprise + local state-owned enterprise&quot; reorganization and integration and the new direction of future central-local joint ventures, which has strong innovation significance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购与重组》、《资本运营》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">壳资源特征；借壳/售壳动因；借壳上市的认定标准；借壳上市的常见模式；产业协同效应；横向并购；央企专业化整合</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
